---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { getPermalink, getBlogPermalink } from '~/utils/permalinks';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About TrendTrack Promo Code — Why This Site Exists',
  description: 'We are a TrendTrack affiliate partner dedicated to helping e-commerce sellers save money with verified promo codes, honest reviews, and in-depth tool comparisons. Learn our story.',
  openGraph: {
    type: 'website',
  },
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 pb-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-primary font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">About Us</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4 font-heading text-heading">
      We help e-commerce sellers save on TrendTrack
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      TrendTrack Promo Code is an independent affiliate website. We are not TrendTrack —
      we are a partner that helps users find the best available discount and decide if TrendTrack is right for them.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading text-heading">Why this site exists</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert text-muted">
        <p>
          When we first started exploring e-commerce intelligence tools, we were overwhelmed by the choices —
          TrendTrack, Minea, PiPiAds, Dropispy, and a dozen others. Pricing was confusing, promo codes were
          scattered across Reddit threads and expired coupon sites, and most "review" pages were just keyword-stuffed
          affiliate pages with no real insight.
        </p>
        <p>
          We built this site to fix that. <strong>One place</strong> where you can find a verified, working
          TrendTrack promo code, read an honest breakdown of what the tool actually does, and compare it head-to-head
          with alternatives — without wading through garbage content.
        </p>
        <p>
          We use TrendTrack ourselves. The promo code <strong>WINNING</strong> on this site is the one we negotiated
          as an affiliate partner, and it gives you 20% off all plans. We test it regularly to make sure it still works.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center font-heading text-heading">What we do</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-[20px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-geist text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#9FE870] text-[#163300] rounded-full font-bold text-xl mb-4 mx-auto">✓</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-heading">Verify Promo Codes</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
          We test the <strong>WINNING</strong> code regularly to confirm it still applies the 20% discount at checkout.
          If it stops working, we update the site immediately.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-[20px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-geist text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#9FE870] text-[#163300] rounded-full font-bold text-xl mb-4 mx-auto">📝</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-heading">Write Honest Guides</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
          From full TrendTrack reviews to product research tutorials, we publish content based on real experience
          with the platform — not reworded marketing copy.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-[20px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-geist text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#9FE870] text-[#163300] rounded-full font-bold text-xl mb-4 mx-auto">⚖️</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-heading">Compare Tools Fairly</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
          Our <a href={getPermalink('/alternatives')} class="text-primary dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">alternatives page</a>
          and head-to-head comparison articles lay out where TrendTrack wins and where competitors like Minea or
          PiPiAds might be a better fit.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Affiliate Disclosure -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto p-6 md:p-8 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-[20px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 font-heading text-heading">How we make money</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert text-muted">
        <p>
          <strong>Transparency matters.</strong> This site is an affiliate partner of TrendTrack. When you use our
          promo code <strong>WINNING</strong> or click our links to sign up, we may earn a commission — at no extra
          cost to you.
        </p>
        <p>
          This does not affect the discount you receive. You still get the full 20% off. The commission comes from
          TrendTrack's side as a referral fee.
        </p>
        <p>
          It also does not affect what we write. If TrendTrack has a limitation, we point it out. If a competitor is
          better for a specific use case, we say so. Our long-term credibility is worth more than any single
          commission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Are Not -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading text-heading">What we are not</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-xl flex-shrink-0">✕</span>
          <p class="text-muted">
            <strong class="text-heading">We are not TrendTrack.</strong>
            This is an independent site. We cannot access your TrendTrack account, process refunds, or change
            subscription pricing. For account issues, contact
            <a href="https://trendtrack.io" class="text-primary dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">TrendTrack directly</a>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-xl flex-shrink-0">✕</span>
          <p class="text-muted">
            <strong class="text-heading">We are not a coupon aggregator.</strong>
            We focus exclusively on TrendTrack. You will not find codes for 50 other tools here — just one tool,
            covered properly.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-xl flex-shrink-0">✕</span>
          <p class="text-muted">
            <strong class="text-heading">We cannot guarantee codes forever.</strong>
            Promo codes can expire or be revoked by TrendTrack at any time. We test ours regularly and update
            the site if anything changes, but we do not control TrendTrack's pricing decisions.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 font-heading text-heading">Ready to save 20%?</h2>
    <p class="text-muted mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Use code <strong>WINNING</strong> at checkout or click below to get started with TrendTrack at the discounted price.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://trendtrack.io?fpr=lanetrendtrack"
      class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#9FE870] text-[#163300] font-bold rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition"
    >
      Claim 20% Off with WINNING →
    </a>
    <p class="mt-6">
      <a href={getBlogPermalink()} class="text-primary dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Read our blog</a>
      for in-depth TrendTrack guides and comparisons.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
